      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though you should expect some minor cosmetic wear, including several scratches on the exterior and some fading on the interior upholstery. All major systems are functional, but it may require routine maintenance soon to keep it running at its best. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
