    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small door dings, and the interior upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will likely need some routine maintenance soon, such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up. Overall, it is a functional and honest vehicle for someone looking for affordable transportation without the need for perfection.",
