    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this car is. It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in the garage and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a dream and is literally spotless inside and out. I'm looking for a quick, smooth sale, so come take a look\u2014you're going to fall in love with it the moment you see it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
