      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative automotive specimen, preserved in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. This vehicle represents the zenith of its production run, exhibiting no discernible wear and maintaining its original, factory-fresh luster. Every mechanical system has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, while the interior remains an untouched sanctuary of luxury. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. We invite a private viewing to appreciate the unrivaled caliber of this offering.",
      "price": 43500.0,
